        <h3>About Me</h3><br><br><br>
        <li id="bio5">
            I am a goal oriented, dedicated, and solution driven person that is catered towards
            collaborating
            with
            individuals and groups to achieve better. I have special interests in the psychological mechanisms that
            underlie the domestic, social, and organizational affairs of society hence why it is my passion to consult
            with groups concerning a broad range of contexts where psychology applies. Aside from my trade I love
            learning, travel, documentaries and spending time with family and friends.
        </li>


